title: 5 Things to Quit
itunes:title: 5 Things to Quit
description:
Episode 534 - Humans get stuck in patterns and habits throughout our lives. The problem with that is that sometimes we pick up habits that actually hold us back from the life that we want. In this episode, I dive into the 5 most toxic habits for you to quit right now!
